        "component": "ContentText",
        "title": "What exactly is halftime?",
        "text": "Halftime was born out of an idea to develop a tool for myself that would make it easier to save and find images, inspirations, and learning materials. I wanted a central place where I could store and view my files. It should also be possible to add details and organize them. While Dropbox is certainly a good option for that, I wanted a simpler user interface and better organization. That's why I decided to create my own solution. The development is still ongoing, but I am already excited about the results."
